text: Norwegian politician Jan-Henrik Fredriksen Jan-Henrik Fredriksen (2 October 1956 – 8 March 2020)Jan-Henrik Fredriksen er død was a Norwegian politician representing the Progress Party (FRP). He was a representative of Finnmark in the Storting He was born in Kragerø, Telemark, and was first elected in 2005. ==Storting committees== *2005-2009 member of the Healthcare committee. ==External links== * * Fremskrittspartiet - Biography ==References== Category:1956 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Progress Party (Norway) politicians Category:Members of the Storting Category:21st-century Norwegian politicians
